 promising growth prospects make it an attractive investment opportunity, prudent risk management and a long-term investment outlook are essential to navigate the volatile nature of the stock market.","Indian investors are rushing to hoard shares of Nvidia amid the AI gold rush, driving a surge in trading volumes. Nvidia was crowned the No. 1 trending stock on Vested Finance, with trading volumes doubling month-on-month. CEO Viram Shah noted a fivefold increase in average trading volume per user compared to last year, reflecting heightened interest in Nvidia's prospects in the AI market.",Business and Finance,2024-02-26 00:00:00
