ss leaders including Jaynagar MP Pratima Mondal faced ‘go back’ slogans when they wanted to meet the parents of the deceased child.","Violence erupted in Jaynagar, West Bengal, after the body of a missing nine-year-old girl was found. Villagers alleged police negligence and claimed the child was sexually assaulted and killed. Angry locals ransacked a police outpost, clashed with police, and blocked roads. One person has been arrested, and a large police contingent was deployed to contain the situation.",Crime and Justice,2024-10-05 00:00:00
